plot: In their latest adventure, the fab four of fun present some of their most catchy and infectious songs to date. Even pop superstar Kylie Minogue goes pink to join The Wiggles to sing Monkey Man. So jump into the jivin' jungle!
title: The Wiggles Go Bananas!
